{"tid":1069106,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老公戴綠帽   後藤真希與姦夫蜜照曝光","createTime":"2019-03-19T17:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T17:57:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f0392d6f2d3bcd222bf4b8c9449aff99a9b1e439","tid":1069106,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T17:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190319/large/1552980623_bf8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190319%2Flarge%2F1552980623_bf8a.jpg&h=0aa1b752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMorning娘的33歲前成員後藤真希，日前爆出偷食醜聞，被雜誌《週刊文春》踢爆背老公偷食28歲前男友。不過事件卻鬧上法庭，事關當後藤真希的老公發現自己戴綠帽後，立即向第三者索償330萬日圓（約21萬港元），繼而令法庭文件得以曝光。<br />\n<br />\n據報道指，後藤真希在陳述書上承認於去年5月兩度跟舊愛發生肉體關係，二人在連鎖式酒店APA Hotel偷情，令後藤真希的賢妻良母形象毀於一旦。雖然後藤真希已於個人網誌撰文回應事件，為不倫戀道歉，又坦承背夫出軌，但否認曾被老公家暴，而《週刊文春》今日就繼續爆料，公開後藤真希與姦夫的LINE短訊對話，又有二人的甜蜜合照。據了解，照片與LINE手機截圖是由男方家人提供，對話是在去年6月8日，疑被家暴的後藤真希寫：「再次哭出來」、「救我」，男方的祖母受訪時指孫兒十分無辜，希望爆料能為孫仔抱不平。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190319/large/1552980636_7cf0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190319%2Flarge%2F1552980636_7cf0.jpg&h=465d36a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a249903e457872b49de4f1d00f6ef606c92a6f48","tid":1069106,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T17:12:07.000Z","msg":"中學嗰時嘅女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MxEXctvonek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMxEXctvonek&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9FJiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=3e3d297f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MxEXctvonek</a>"},{"pid":"1bc39b17e22eb5d83fe929e3943c47ef192bf736","tid":1069106,"uid":2111,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T17:16:45.000Z","msg":"臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\